763
00:41:26.614 --> 00:41:29.051
Your mom has a GPS
tracker on your phone.

764
00:41:29.182 --> 00:41:30.400
I know.

765
00:41:30.618 --> 00:41:32.838
I should've moved around more.

766
00:41:34.013 --> 00:41:35.971
But. Daddy...

767
00:41:36.145 --> 00:41:37.625
He's so fucking hot.

768
00:41:37.843 --> 00:41:39.584
No. no. no. That's the truth.

769
00:41:39.714 --> 00:41:44.066
He was reading Bible stories
and I just got lost in 'em.

770
00:41:45.328 --> 00:41:46.328
- All right.
- Mm-hmm.

771
00:41:46.373 --> 00:41:47.853
Good girl.

772
00:41:49.811 --> 00:41:51.813
I love you. Daddy.

773
00:43:30.129 --> 00:43:31.739
Hold that thought.

774
00:44:27.012 --> 00:44:30.276
Ariana. this isn't
an attempt to coerce you.

775
00:44:30.493 --> 00:44:32.931
We are trying to help
you and your son.

776
00:44:33.105 --> 00:44:36.238
I think it's worth
pointing out if you refuse.

777
00:44:36.412 --> 00:44:39.764
we will be forced to withhold
payment to the other families.

778
00:44:40.721 --> 00:44:42.046
The other families signed.

779
00:44:42.070 --> 00:44:43.768
They signed an agreement

780
00:44:43.942 --> 00:44:45.508
that we have yet to sign.

781
00:44:45.683 --> 00:44:47.423
Because we are waiting on you.

782
00:44:47.597 --> 00:44:49.034
Agreement to sign what?

783
00:44:55.083 --> 00:44:58.913
That didn't take long. This
is a private matter. sir.

784
00:45:00.088 --> 00:45:02.874
I'd like him to see it.

785
00:45:04.789 --> 00:45:06.486
Would you look at this for me?

786
00:45:07.313 --> 00:45:08.575
Yeah.

787
00:45:15.843 --> 00:45:16.975
And you are...?

788
00:45:18.280 --> 00:45:19.280
Cooper.

789
00:45:19.325 --> 00:45:20.848
"Cooper."

790
00:45:22.850 --> 00:45:24.199
Cooper Norris?

791
00:45:26.288 --> 00:45:27.637
Yes. ma'am.

792
00:45:33.905 --> 00:45:37.125
We've been looking
everywhere for you.

793
00:45:37.299 --> 00:45:39.780
<i>♪ "Moment of Truth" by
The Red Clay Strays ♪</i>

794
00:45:44.611 --> 00:45:46.874
<i>♪ Why do I do ♪</i>

795
00:45:47.048 --> 00:45:52.010
<i>♪ All of these things
I shouldn't do? ♪</i>

796
00:45:52.140 --> 00:45:56.362
<i>♪ Why do I stumble ♪</i>

797
00:45:56.579 --> 00:45:59.669
<i>♪ When I'm somewhere
close to you? ♪</i>

798
00:45:59.800 --> 00:46:02.890
<i>♪ If I can't be righteous ♪</i>
